en-US.title: Village Medical: Primary Care for Transgender Community
en-US.description: Village Medical, a patient-oriented medical facility, is committed to providing healthcare that caters to the unique needs of the transgender community, offering services such as annual check-ups, diagnostic testing, illness and injury treatment, medication management, and specialist referrals. We prioritize a personalized approach to ensure our patients receive the best care and attention they need.

address: 600 N Shepherd Dr 5 530, Houston, TX 77007, USA
